Class LimaCharlie

  • java.lang.Object
    • LimaCharlie
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EDR

    public class LimaCharlie
extends java.lang.Object
implements EDR
    LimaCharlie Class implements the EDR Interface The class is used to send commands to LimaCharlie using its Python API. This is achieved by executing the python scripts available.
